  Please enter a number up to the maximum amount (£<%= number_with_delimiter(calculator.tuition_fee_maximum_full_time) %> for full-time, £<%= number_with_delimiter(calculator.tuition_fee_maximum_part_time) %> for part-time), don’t enter ‘£’
<% end %>
